      "message": "mining: default coinbase commitment option off\n\nSet always_add_coinbase_commitment to false by default. Empty block\ntemplates and templates without SegWit spends no longer include an\nunnecessary coinbase witness and SegWit OP_RETURN.\n\nNo known IPC mining client relies on the previous dummy commitment\nbehavior, and omitting it is the better default. Keep RPC block\ngeneration and getblocktemplate behavior unchanged by opting those\ncallers in explicitly.",
